{"tid":1580063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海關扣查美容院膠手套 疑為封殺示威「一網打盡」無辜商戶","createTime":"2019-09-19T01:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T11:13:22.000Z","uid":68738,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ee50acc62a414761da431941901c19f138697a84","tid":1580063,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190918/large/1568799502_be92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190918%2Flarge%2F1568799502_be92.jpg&h=763cc085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳小姐（化名）質疑，網上流傳香港海關加強出入口管制，除一般違禁品外，其他敏感貨品也禁運。<br />\n<br />\n政府全方位打壓示威，有美容院東主向《蘋果》表示，約3周前從內地商戶訂購用完即棄PVC膠手套，可於為客人做推拿或按摩時穿上；但至今未仍收到貨品，致電物流公司查詢，獲回覆指貨品被香港海關扣查。網上流傳反送中示威爆發後，海關加強出入口管制，甚至毛巾、手套、口罩及雨傘也禁運，她質疑海關為打壓示威，而一網打盡扣查一般商人進口的貨品。<br />\n<br />\n陳小姐（化名）表示，其美容院一向有從內地商戶訂購用完即棄PVC膠手套，以往訂貨後3至4日便收到貨品，每次訂10至20盒。膠手套是用於為客人做按摩或推拿時穿戴。她指，約3周前訂購10盒共100隻手套，約200港元，但至今仍未收到貨品。她致電訂貨商戶，商戶指已發貨；再致電物流公司查詢，獲回覆指貨品已運抵港，但被香港海關扣留。其間美容院也有從內地訂購不同貨品，在正常時間內收貨，沒有類似問題。<br />\n<br />\n陳小姐質疑，網上流傳香港海關加強出入口管制，除一般違禁品外，其他敏感貨品也禁運，包括毛巾、雨傘、旗幟、旗桿、宣傳橫額、黑色衫、鋼管、手套、口罩、手電筒、彈弓、鋼珠、弓箭、高壓氣體噴射器，均被香港海關列為禁運物品。有內地物流公司發出的溫馨提示更指，若貨品被海關扣查，客人需自行承擔損失。陳小姐懷疑她訂的手套被海關扣查，是海關想打壓示威，令一般商人進口的貨品也受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190918/60058272?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F60058272%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5corGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=7763cb47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F60058272%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=ec242824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190918/60058272?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"50eb639943bce2406b825f21b7c3bb44b5f7b768","tid":1580063,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:27:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5corGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=7ffa2e2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5corGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=4a2e634a\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"f99ba59f5f9ca1628a7cec64f28f56f6a5291697","tid":1580063,"uid":134415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"幾時入醫院拉曬D醫生護士?"},{"pid":"de3c85877cd91d7789bf0b8d42ba7dec0728b2c5","tid":1580063,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:28:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-larg